>\n可能你會話法國車無地方整<br />\n不過依家 d 新車頭5年真係無乜野壞<br />\n除非真係有 factory defect / design fault 之外<br />\n應該真係換油換下消耗品已經 OK<br />\n<br />\n所以岩 budget 既就買啦<br />\n呢個價位得 Polo，但新一代就出<br />\n唔通買 Spade 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feb0451a8b4b02692c6457f522b00630923e097","tid":455650,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鐘意呢個款做咩唔諗gti?</blockquote><br />\n因為好怕壞波箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nClio GT 個 EDC Gearbox 同 VW DSG 一樣係雙離合<br />\n唔識揸一樣會揸壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197897aeb5d83891afaec3c9dbccb468dab0dfdb","tid":455650,"uid":136303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想平平地買架車仔，代步返工之餘又有少少嘢玩下，無意中見到呢部。但係基本上係街無見過，想睇下有無巴打揸過，用後感覺如何，多唔多嘢整，同埋要整係咪好煩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nClio GT 岩岩 facelift 左<br />\n頭燈 LED 夠靚仔<br />\n新車都係 17 18 萬<br />\n年尾應該可以再減<br />\n雖則係雷諾法國廠<br />\n但好多 parts 已經係用返日產 parts<br />\n成副偈都係日產偈<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話法國車無地方整<br />\n不過依家 d 新車頭5年真係無乜野壞<br />\n除非真係有 factory defect / design fault 之外<br />\n應該真係換油換下消耗品已經 OK<br />\n<br />\n所以岩 budget 既就買啦<br />\n呢個價位得 Polo，但新一代就出<br />\n唔通買 Spade 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打，巴打有揸過？可唔可以講埋後座坐得舒唔舒服？有時要車埋屋企人。其實真係好吸引我，只係好奇怪點解咁少人揸呢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通真係揸哂spade? Spade真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eec7554408276fb8f33d87a705fd254269d0ec2","tid":455650,"uid":136303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鐘意呢個款做咩唔諗gti?</blockquote><br />\n因為好怕壞波箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nClio GT 